cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.CL, cs.NE 

The paper proposes a few-shot classification method using meta-learning on multiple heterogeneous domains. This involves designing each model to have its own per-layer modulator with a base network shared by others, which is inspired by multi-task learning techniques. Therefore, the paper is likely to belong to the following arXiv CS sub-categories: 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning)
- cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition)
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence)
- cs.CL (Computation and Language)
- cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing)
